AddToFunc   FuncFvwmMail
+ I  FuncFvwmRunInXterm "Mail" "mail"

DestroyFunc FuncFvwm2Mail
AddToFunc   FuncFvwm2Mail
+ I FuncFvwmRunInXterm "Mail" "mutt"

DestroyFunc FuncFvwm3Mail
